         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">16/6/90. ¶  ¶ I ought to have written to you long ago, honoured Friend, to thank you for the avid interest that you still take in the advancement of the study of the algae of Australia, as this partic...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">90.06.16a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. <seg style="">Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">16/6/90.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Längst hätte ich mich Ihnen schriftlich nahen sollen, verehrter Freund, um Ihnen für das rege Interesse zu danken, welches Sie noch immer nehmen an der Förderung der Algenkunde Australiens, wie dies besonders in neuester Zeit wieder aus Ihrer </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">präch</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">tigen Bearbeitung von <name key="Sargassum">Sargassum</name> hervorgeht.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es ist auch recht erfreulich, dass die neuen Funde bei Champion-Bay sich so wichtig erwiesen. Ich habe Aussicht mehr Material aus der Champion-Bay zu bekommen durch etwas Geld-Aufwand und die gütige Hülfe eines mir befreundeten dortigen Arztes.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die von Ihnen zurück kommenden Exemplare werden hier ein immer werthvoller Beitrag für Studien in der von mir gestifteten Anstalt bleiben.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend und Ihnen alles Gute wünschend Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">16/6/90.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I ought to have written to you long ago, honoured Friend, to thank you for the avid interest that you still take in the advancement of the study of the algae of Australia, as this particularly emerges again recently from your <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">splendid</hi>
               </seg> treatment of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Sargassum">Sargassum</name>
               </seg>.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Agardh (1889). M to J. Agardh, 9 May 1890 (in this edition as 90-05-09a) includes thanks for sending the work.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is also very pleasing to me that the new finds near Champion Bay prove so important.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See J. Agardh to M, 4 May 1890, with identifications of two collections from Champion Bay, WA.</p>
               </note> I have prospects to get more material from Champion Bay through some expenditure of money and the kind help of a physician there friendly to me.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Dr Charles Elliott.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The specimens coming back from you will always remain a valuable contribution for studies here in the institution founded by me.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully and wishing you every good thing</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Sargassum">Sargassum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
